<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='156:182'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0023', 'WYG', '000-1a' );" name="000-1a" class="pb">[000-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='182:197'>欽定四庫全書　　　　經部四</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='197:220'>　周官禄田考　　　　　禮類一<span class='krp-note'>周禮之屬/</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='220:226'>　　提要</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='226:246'>　　　　<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>等謹案周官禄田考三卷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='246:269'>　　　國朝沈彤撰彤以班禄之法自宋歐陽修有周</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='269:292'>　　　　禮官多田少禄且不給之疑後人多從其説</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='292:315'>　　　　即有辨者不過以攝官為詞彤獨詳究周制</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='315:338'>　　　　以與之辨因撰是書為官爵數公田數禄田</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='338:364'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0023', 'WYG', '000-1b' );" name="000-1b" class="pb">[000-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='364:387'>　　　　數三篇凡田爵禄之數不見於經者或求諸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='387:410'>　　　　註不見於註者則據經起例推闡旁通補經</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='410:433'>　　　　所無乃適如經之所有其説精宻淹通於鄭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='433:456'>　　　　賈註疏以後可云特出其中間有未安者如</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='456:479'>　　　　謂子男之國不得有中士考孟子稱小國地</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='479:502'>　　　　方五十里有中士倍下士之文趙岐註曰子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='502:525'>　　　　男為小國王制曰王者之制禄爵公侯伯子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='525:548'>　　　　男凡五等諸侯之上大夫卿下大夫上士中</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='548:574'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0023', 'WYG', '000-2a' );" name="000-2a" class="pb">[000-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='574:597'>　　　　士下士凡五等孔頴達疏謂諸侯統公侯伯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='597:620'>　　　　子男則子男有中士矣王制又曰若有中士</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='620:643'>　　　　下士數各居其上之三分鄭註上中下士二</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='643:666'>　　　　十七人各三分之周禮太宰賈疏釋此文謂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='666:689'>　　　　朝聘之位次國之上士當大國之中士中士</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='689:712'>　　　　當下士下士當其空小國之上士當次國之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='712:735'>　　　　中士中士當下士下士當其空故云各居其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='735:758'>　　　　上之三分若子男無中士則小國之士不敷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='758:784'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0023', 'WYG', '000-2b' );" name="000-2b" class="pb">[000-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='784:807'>　　　　三分之數與經文戾矣彤又謂加田之制國</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='807:830'>　　　　八十里者其加田極於百里四十里者極於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='830:853'>　　　　五十里二十里者極於二十五里考司勲文</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='853:876'>　　　　曰凡賞地無常輕重視功又曰惟加田無征</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='876:899'>　　　　鄭註加田既賞之又加賜以田夫賞田且無</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='899:923'>　　　　常數况加田乎春秋宣十五年𫝊晉侯賞桓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='923:947'>　　　　子狄臣千室又賞士伯以𤓰衍之縣襄三十</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='947:971'>　　　　六年𫝊三月甲寅享子展賜之以先輅三命</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='971:997'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0023', 'WYG', '000-3a' );" name="000-3a" class="pb">[000-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='997:1021'>　　　　之服先八邑襄二十七年𫝊公與免餘邑六</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='1021:1045'>　　　　十襄二十八年𫝊與晏子弼殿其鄙六十此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='1045:1068'>　　　　無論其為賞為加率無常數正可與司勲文</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='1068:1092'>　　　　相證而彤定以二十里十里五里稽諸經𫝊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='1092:1115'>　　　　畧無明文又彤算畿内百萬井去山陵林麓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='1115:1138'>　　　　之等三十六萬井存田六十四萬井以為三</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='1138:1161'>　　　　分去一本於班固刑法志今考百萬井而去</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='1161:1184'>　　　　三十六萬井乃二十五分而去九班志本不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='1184:1210'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0023', 'WYG', '000-3b' );" name="000-3b" class="pb">[000-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1210:1233'>　　　　云三分去一彤所引殊為誤記且班志非為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1233:1256'>　　　　周官作註故立算不必盡據經文今彤既據</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1256:1279'>　　　　經文即當參校經義求其脗合考鄭載師註</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1279:1302'>　　　　算近郊百里則用三分去一之法算六遂以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1302:1325'>　　　　外則用十八分去五之法葢近郊以内不易</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1325:1348'>　　　　之地家百畆一易之地家二百畆再易之地</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1348:1371'>　　　　家三百畆相通三夫而受六夫之地至六遂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1371:1394'>　　　　以外上地家百畆菜百畆下地家百畆菜二</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1394:1420'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0023', 'WYG', '000-4a' );" name="000-4a" class="pb">[000-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1420:1443'>　　　　百畆相通六夫而受十三夫之地其所受之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1443:1466'>　　　　田既較近郊為加多則所去之地即當較近</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1466:1489'>　　　　郊為加少故郊内三分去一而遂外僅十八</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1489:1512'>　　　　分去五也夫以三分去一算遂外之地且猶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1512:1535'>　　　　病其過多而况於二十五分而去九乎此不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='1535:1558'>　　　　信鄭註之所以疎也至謂遂人十夫亦為井</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='1558:1581'>　　　　田乃襲宋人緒論尤無足置辨厯來攷周禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='1581:1604'>　　　　為偽者不止一家惟官多田少之説猝難置</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='1604:1630'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0023', 'WYG', '000-4b' );" name="000-4b" class="pb">[000-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='1630:1653'>　　　　辨得彤此書遂决千古之疑頗為有功於經</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='1653:1676'>　　　　典惟此數條乃其百慮之一失故附著之俾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='1676:1699'>　　　　論者有所考焉乾隆四十二年六月恭校上</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='1699:1731'>　　　　　　　總纂官<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>紀昀<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>陸錫熊<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>孫士毅</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='1731:1756'>　　　　　　　總　校　官　<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>　陸　費　墀</span><br/>
</p>
